Those big-nosed oneshad come back to Earth to first take over some kind ofunderground harvesting operation.” - Kansas Abductee Symbols and craft shapes seen in mind of Kansas man while in the presenceof tall, blue-eyed blond-haired humanoids. Drawing © 2007 by Kansas abductee.Return to Part 1July 31, 2007 Albuquerque, New Mexico - The Kansas abductee told me, “Tall, scalybeings with very large noses – bigger than Arabic – and yellow eyes with vertical pupilslike cat eyes. Those big-nosed ones (in the images shown to me) had come back to Earthto first take over some kind of underground harvesting operation.”Twenty-eight years ago, I first investigated the global animal mutilation mystery in the fallof 1979 for the television documentary special, A Strange Harvest, at KMGH-TV (CBSaffiliate then) in Denver, Colorado. Law enforcement are the ones who told me first, offthe record, that the perpetrators were "from outer space." A Strange Harvest was firstbroadcast as a 2-hour special on May 25, 1980. Nine years later, I had produced my firstbook, An Alien Harvest: Further Evidence Linking Animal Mutilations and HumanAbductions to Alien Life Forms © 1989. (See Earthfiles Shop.) By then, I had heardfrom law enforcement and ranchers who had seen red-orange "flaming" spheres or beamsof light where later a mutilated animal would be found. I even heard from someeyewitnesses who described seeing a calf, or cow, or bull rising in beams of light - orlowered in beams of light. Those animals would have the same bloodless excisions oftissue: an ear, eyeball, circular hide around the eye, jaw flesh, tongue removed deep withinthroat and sometimes larynx and esophagus excised as well. Udder or penis and testicles

wholly removed or pieces removed and in almost all of the animal mutilations, the rectumis cored out (in females the vaginal tract is usually excised along with the rectal tissue.)Eventually I talked with military and intelligence people off the record, who confirmedthat extraterrestrial biological entities are the perpetrators of the worldwide animalmutilation mystery - a "genetic harvest," it was explained. But a genetic harvest for whatpurpose? And by exactly which specific non-human entities? I had interviewedeyewitnesses who had seen blond-haired beings down beside a cow excising tissue (See: 040306 Earthfiles Genetic Harvest in Cimarron, New Mexico?)In Colorado back in the 1970s, cowboys reported seeing "grey things" float over a corralfence into a collection of cattle where a mutilated cow was found. Also in Colorado, onefemale eyewitness told me she encountered a "standing up alligator" in broad daylightwhen she was out riding her horse. Subsequently other eyewitnesses in Colorado andFlorida have described being taken aboard discs where "standing up alligators or lizards"demonstrate the removal of tissue and fluid from cows for reptilian food.What is never clear to anyone, including the human abductees: What is the relationshipbetween the blond beings, the gray entities and the cat-eyed reptiles? Are they workingtogether on some huge genetic harvest for survival reasons? Or is Earth life being used as agenetic supermarket for many applications?Or are those three types in conflict? If in conflict, what is the argument - or war? - about?This is what the Kansas abductee thinks might be happening, based on 3-dimensionalimages "projected" into his mind while in the presence of another unidentified intelligencein 1992 or 1993 when he was thirty-two or thirty-three.Kansas Abductee, now 47-years-old and requesting anonymity: "The first image I wasshown was a giant rectangle-shaped craft orbiting around the Earth. You could see theEarth and this ship in the image at the same time.THIS IS THE BIG RECTANGLE WITH HOLES IN IT IN YOUR DRAWING?Right, and this thing is just massive.Massive rectangular craft with "portholes" on the side and five larger circlesat one end were glowing blue-white as if the propulsion source. Discs flew out of the bottomof the rectangular craft and flew toward Earth. Drawing © 2007 by Kansas abductee.COLOR?Dark.DARK IN A BLUE DAYLIGHT SKY? OR NIGHT?Outer space.ARE YOU SEEING THE BIG RECTANGLE-SHAPED SHIP ON A 3-DIMENSIONALHOLOGRAPHIC SCREEN INSIDE A NON-HUMAN CRAFT?I’m not sure how I’m seeing it. It’s almost like I’m seeing it in my mind because I don’tremember being on the ship.ARE YOU ASLEEP IN BED? WHERE ARE YOU?I remember going to sleep that night and waking up that next morning just in a panic.

WHAT AGE?1992 or 1993, so 32 or 33 years oldIS YOUR MILD FILLED WITH IMAGES?Ye s .CAN YOU GIVE ME A NARRATIVE ABOUT THOSE IMAGES?It started off like I was outside this ship looking toward the Earth. You could see it plainand you could see the massive rectangle-shaped craft, which appeared to have four smallerand one larger center engine that had a bluish-white glow. There was no roar or sound.Down the side of it appeared portholes that were lighted up. As I got closer, somedisc-shaped objects were exiting through the bottom of that rectangle-shaped craft.WERE THOSE CRAFT EXITING TOWARD EARTH DISC-SHAPED AND NOTTRIANGULAR-SHAPED?Ye s .YOU ASSOCIATE THE DISCS WITH WHAT?The nearest thing I associate them with would be like fighters. Big Nosed Reptilians in Rectangle CraftWHICH TYPE OF INTELLIGENCE IS IN THE DISCS COMING OUT OF THE HUGERECTANGULAR-SHAPED CRAFT?The impression I got was that they are the larger-nosed grey individuals with the cat eyes,a yellowish eye with a black vertical pupil like a cat's.THE NOSE – IS IT BIGGER THAN WE ASSOCIATE WITH ARABIC NOSES?Ye s .CAN YOU DESCRIBE THE CHEEK BONES, CHIN, FOREHEAD, NECK?If you colored the Geico lizard (TV commercials) pine tree green and put cat eyes on him,that’s pretty much what they look like.HOW TALL?The glimpses I got was sitting in the ship, which was big enough to hold two or three6-foot-tall men. So, I’m going to say the Big Nosed ones were probably 5 feet tall.WERE THEY MUSCULAR?They were pretty well built. I wouldn’t say muscular, but they weren’t spindly either. Theylooked kind of like a crocodile body, pretty hefty.THE GEICO LIZARD IS NOT AN ALIGATOR. DO YOU MEAN THE FACE ANDHEAD WERE SHAPED LIKE A LIZARD, BUT THE BODY WAS LIKE ANALIGATOR WITH THICKER SKIN AND SCALES?They had suits on.WHAT WERE THOSE SUITS LIKE?Pale green, form-fitting. Came up over the head so that just the eyes and the snout werereally all you could see.WAS THE SNOUT THE SAME COLOR AS THE BODY COVERING?No, it was not the olive green color of the covering they had on.WHAT IS THE COLOR OF THE 'ALIGATOR-SCALY' SNOUT?Pine tree green.SO, DARK GREEN?

Yeah, but it’s a low light situation where I’m seeing him.WERE THE SNOUT SCALES LIKE AN EARTH ALIGATOR’S?Pretty much, yeah, except the snout is not that long.SO, IT’S MORE THE SHAPE OF A LIZARD’S SNOUT, BUT WITH THE SCALES OF ACROCODILE.Pretty much, yeah.HOW MANY FINGERS ON HANDS?The hands seemed to be covered in the olive green material like a glove. But the thumbwas real short. The fingers were kind of short, too, and there were four fingers, but kind ofstubby. When I clearly saw the hand, it was laying in a silver metallic-looking hand printon a slanted panel that his hand fit in.LIKE A CONTROLLER PANEL?Right. Like that’s how they controlled the craft. The panel was on a 45-degree angle rightbetween two of the alligator pilots - that’s the only way I know how to describe them.They were flying the disc. In front of the one was a concave front to the panel. He waskind of leaning back where he was sitting, his feet were down resting on what lookedalmost like the floorboard of a car. The curved panel came up at a 45-degree angle in frontof the one that had its 4-fingered right hand on the silver hand print embedded in thepanel. The panel also had some lights in it. I couldn’t see his left hand. The other pilot wasdoing something else.WHAT COLOR WAS THE PANEL?Dark color.SO, THE HANDPRINT LOOKS LIKE A SILVER HANDPRINT AT GRAUMAN’SCHINESE THEATER IN HOLLYWOOD?Right."Sidewalk of the Stars" outside Grauman's Chinese Theatre inHollywood, California. Myrna Loy placed her hands and shoes in this cement in 1936.DOES THE ALLIGATOR PILOT LIFT HIS RIGHT HAND OUT OF THAT EMBEDDEDHAND PRINT AND THAT’S HOW YOU SEE THE SILVER COLOR?No, I’d say the silver color surrounded his hand in the hand print by about ¼ inch all theway round his hand.HOW BIG WAS HIS HAND?His stubby fingers were about 1.5 inches long. They were shorter than my fingers - maybeabout half the length of mine.ANY NAILS OR CLAWS AT THE END OF HIS FINGERS?I could not see because there was that olive green glove-like covering over the hand.WHERE ARE YOU WATCHING?Back behind the pilot in front of the panel. I kind of felt like I was remote viewing.DID THEY REGISTER ANY CONSCIOUSNESS OF YOU IN WHATEVER FORM YOUWERE IN?

No, it was like they didn’t have a clue. "Life-threatening Danger"WHAT DID YOU SENSE WAS THE INTENT OF THE BIG NOSEDLIZARD/ALLIGATOR CREATURES?Danger. Life threatening danger.ANY TELEPATHIC COMMUNICATION FROM NON-HUMANS ABOUT WHAT ITWAS THE BIG NOSED REPTILES WANTED TO DO?The only thing I can remember consciously is the lizard things were attacking.WHAT HAPPENS NEXT IN THE IMAGES?I found myself in the middle of what looked like bombed out land like WWII. There werethese lizard-looking things herding humans.HOW ARE THEY HERDING HUMANS? WHAT CONTROL DID THEY HAVE?There was a lot of smoke and fire, a lot of buildings crumbled. My thought was that the bignosed lizard types had some weapons, but I did not see any. So, if they did, they were notlike a conventional weapon we humans have.ARE YOU SEEING THE BIG NOSE LIZARDS HOLDING ON TO PEOPLES’ ARMS?Yes, pretty much with force. What I saw was about fifteen or twenty of them in aV-formation pushing people along. If someone fell, they would just pick them up andthrow them.SO THEY WERE EXTREMELY HOSTILE?Yes. People were very scared for some reason. Nobody seemed to be resisting. I took itthat the lizard things used some kind of force so that nobody wanted to mess with them. Blue-Eyed Blonds - Passive in Reptile Attack?WHERE ARE THE BLUE-EYED BLONDS IN ALL OF THIS?The next thing I come to is that I’m shown that the blonds have people, but they aregentle. It’s almost like they are trying to hide some humans, trying to help them.WHY AREN’T THE BLONDS FIGHTING THE BIG NOSED LIZARDS?I don’t know. That was just the next scene I got flashed to. Then, the next scene was amilitary battle that was not going very well for our side.WHAT WERE WE TRYING TO DO?Defend against an attack. There were canons going off, there was automatic gunfire. Theonly clear recollection I have is there is an explosion and one of the discs flips like it’s outof control. Then it gained control and flew by. It was almost like I was being shown thatwe humans are going to try to defend ourselves, but there is no defense (against thereptiles). Underground HarvestingThe next scene is where I’m shown some underground facilities that we humans areworking in as forced labor and the lizard things are harvesting something. I’m not sure – Ididn’t get a good look at it.WHO IS DOING THE HARVESTING?I saw an underground facility where the lizard things were in control. The human ‘slaves’all seemed to be old and young men. I didn’t see any women.SO, THERE ARE HUMANS WORKING UNDERGROUND WHERE THE BIG NOSED

LIZARDS ARE AND HUMANS ARE DOING WORK FOR THOSE LIZARDS?Right.WHAT KIND OF WORK?They are harvesting.W H AT D O E S T H AT M E A N ?It’s not like they are mining or digging. It was some distance away, but it looked like theywere opening some kind of bag in a honeycomb and being very careful with what theywere taking out. I could not clearly see what was being taken out, but to me it looked likea cocoon of some kind. I don’t know.WHEN YOU SAY HONEYCOMB, WHAT DOES THAT MEAN?Like miles of tunnels with these things on the sides the human slaves were taking down.HONEYCOMBS ARE 6-SIDED WALLS IN HONEYCOMBS. ARE YOU SEEING6-SIDED SHAPES NEXT TO EACH OTHER LIKE A HIVE?I see some kind of shape and I say honeycomb because that’s the only thing I can relate itto. Didn’t exactly look like a honeycomb, but it was some type of pattern or formation.IT WAS ORGANIC?I don’t know if it was organic or cut into the rock. This was just a quick flash because anylonger than that I could have been detected.DETECTION OF YOU AS A REMOTE VIEWER?Right. I got the feeling that this harvesting in those tunnels was the main project, thereason the lizard things are back here.THAT THE BIG NOSED REPTILES HAVE BEEN USING THOUSANDS OF TUNNELSUNDERGROUND ON OUR PLANET TO PRODUCE SOMETHING THAT MIGHT BEAN ORGANIC LIFE FORM THAT IS INSIDE OF SOMETHING THAT LOOKED LIKEA COCOON INSIDE SOME KIND OF HONEY COMB FILLING THE WALLS OF THETUNNELS AND THAT THE BIG NOSED REPTILES HAD RETURNED TO HARVEST?Right. And that is what humans were originally designed to do.WERE THE BLUE-EYED BLONDS THE ONES SHOWING THIS TO YOU?I'm not sure.DID WHATEVER WAS SHOWING YOU THE IMAGES IN YOUR MIND EXPLAIN TOYOU TELEPATHICALLY WHAT WAS GOING ON?I remember just the danger aspect. The aspect that it all had to be stopped before it beganor we were not going to be able to stop it. I remember having the feeling that ourgovernment knew a little bit about what was going on, but did not know the whole story.So, therefore, authorities were thinking that as long as they helped (reptiles) out,everything was going to be fine. Kansas Abductee Senses Time Lineof Tunnel Events Between 2007 and 2009Then the big nosed things turned the tables on the human authorities. And the coming ofthe big nosed reptiles is imminent, in the near future.THE COMING OF THE BIG NOSED LIZARDS IS IMMINENT WHEN?From the buildings I saw destroyed and the cars, the vehicles that I saw, looked prettymuch like what we’re seeing today. So, I associate it with pretty soon. I have the feelingthat within the next couple of years, they are going to make their presence known andafter that, all heck is going to break loose.YOU ARE SEEING BUILDINGS AND CARS DESTROYED AND SOME HUMANMILITARY EFFORTS THAT ARE NOT HAVING ANY IMPACTS ON THE BIG NOSEDDISCS. WHAT IS THE NEXT IMAGE?

The next image after that was the honeycomb in the tunnels image. After that was theblond-haired, blue-eyed people assisting the humans. I don’t know if that’s after the lizardthings have left, or during the attack and the blonds are trying to hide people, or exactlywhen that is because these images were like cut up. It was not like a film reel in sequencethat gave me a complete chronological event. It was, ‘You need to see this, you need tosee this, over and over.'WHAT WAS THE NEXT IMAGE AFTER THE BLUE-EYED BLONDS HELPINGHUMANS?That was probably the most disturbing because it looked like in all big cities an atomicbomb had gone off. There were people just kind of wandering around in a daze. But thiswas Earth-wide. The next image after that was the large craft backing off.THE BIG RECTANGULAR ONE WITH PORTHOLES AND LIGHTS?Right.THAT IS DEFINITELY THE BIG NOSED LIZARD’S CARRIER THAT SHOWS UPWITH ALL THE SMALLER DISCS THAT LEAVE IT AND COME TO EARTH FROM?Right.SO, YOU SEE THE BIG RECTANGULAR CRAFT MOVING OFF. WHAT DO YOUINTERPRET THAT TO MEAN?As it’s moving off, it’s turning so that the front of it is rotating towards the Earth. That wasthe last image I got. I don’t know if that meant that they were turning to leave, or turningto finish us off. Why Wouldn't Blonds Fight Reptiles?WHY DIDN’T THE BLUE-EYED BLONDS TAKE ON THE BIG NOSED LIZARDS?I don’t know. I don’t know the whole fight. Maybe they did?BUT YOU THINK YOU WERE SHOWN GLIMPSES OF OUR FUTURE ON EARTH.SO IF YOU WERE SEEING DESTRUCTION OF BUILDINGS AND CARS AND THEUNDERGROUND TUNNELS WHERE HUMANS WERE HERDED BY THE BIGNOSED LIZARDS, THEN THAT MEANS THE ATTACK OCCURRED.WHY WOULDN’T THE BLOND, BLUE-EYED HUMANOIDS THAT HAVE BEENDEALING WITH YOU SINCE YOU WERE 8-YEARS-OLD HAVE PREVENTED THEBIG NOSED ATTACK IN THE FIRST PLACE?The only feeling I get is that the blond people know something that we don’t and maybethey are going to help regenerate the Earth? Or the Big Nosed had some kind of militarydevice? I don’t know why the blonds didn’t come right out and fight the lizard things.ISN’T IT CONTRADICTORY THAT THE BLOND, BLUE-EYED BEINGS TELL YOUTHAT ‘EVERYTHING WILL BE ALL RIGHT’ AND THE BIG NOSED LIZARDSWANT THE EARTH FOR SOMETHING. IF THE BLOND, BLUE-EYED ARE ALSOADVANCED INTELLIGENCES, WHY WOULD THEY HAVE EVER ALLOWED THEBIG NOSED LIZARDS TO HAVE ANY FOOTHOLD ON EARTH IN THE FIRSTPLACE?I have to relate this to Biblical things that maybe there is a bigger plan here that I haven’tbeen shown. Maybe this has to happen for a reason, maybe so the blond, blue-eyed peoplecan finally make the Earth a peaceful place to live.HAVE YOU EVER BEEN SHOWN ANYTHING ABOUT THE FATE OF THE BIGNOSED LIZARDS?No, but I have a feeling they are in for a big surprise.FROM?I don’t know. I just don’t think they are going to get away with it totally.WHERE ARE THE BIG NOSED LIZARDS FROM?That drawing of mine that shows a planet – it’s not in our solar system, but the Hubble will

take photographs of it.Origin of the big nosed reptilians, dot inside circle.Drawing © 2007 by Kansas abductee.WHAT IS THE THING THAT HAS ALL THE RINGS?I think it’s a planet.WHAT’S THE CIRCLE WITH THE DOT IN THE MIDDLE?I think that’s where the lizard creatures are from.THE TWO CIRCLES, ONE ABOVE THE OTHER – WHAT IS THAT?I believe those are like smaller planets or moons that identify their planet.BELOW THAT IS A TRIANGLE THAT HAS THREE DOTS IN IT, A TRIANGLE THATHAS ONE DOT IN IT, A STAR OF DAVID THAT HAS A DOT INSIDE AND A DOTABOVE IT, A TRIANGLE WITH A BROKEN BASE WITH A DOT AND LINE, ANDTHEN THE OMEGA SYMBOL WITH A DOT. WHO DO YOU ASSOCIATE THOSESYMBOLS WITH IN TERMS OF THE NON-HUMAN TYPES AND WHAT DO THEYMEAN?Symbols drawn from mental image memory by Kansas abductee.I associate those with the blond-haired, blue-eyed people. I’m not exactly sure what theymean. I’m not clear.WHERE DID YOU SEE THEM?Those were what I drew that morning after the mist was over me. I’m not sure when orhow I saw them. (Part 1)AS YOU DREW THEM, WHAT WAS THE ASSOCIATION IN YOUR MIND? WHATKIND OF FEELING?Peace and harmony.THEN YOU HAVE A DRAWING OF THREE TRIANGULAR CRAFT AND YOUWROTE ‘SIGN?’ WHAT IS THAT ALL ABOUT?

Triangular-shaped aerial craft headed toward Earth.Drawing © 2007 by Kansas abductee.That’s an image burned into my mind. I’m not sure what it is, except it’s somethingcoming. I think the circle is the Earth and the triangles are something getting closer.ARE THE TRIANGLES ASSOCIATED WITH THE BIG-NOSED LIZARDS INADDITION TO THE DISKS?No, I think they are associated with something else. It’s a mystery to me. I don’t get anyfeeling except peace.ARE THE TRIANGLES OCCUPIED BY THE BLOND, BLUE-EYED HUMANOIDS?I don’t know. I just get the feeling of peace and well being.TO THE LEFT OF THE TRIANGLE CRAFT ‘SIGN,’ YOU HAVE 3 PARALLEL LINES.AND BETWEEN TWO PARALLEL LINES ARE 3 DOTS AND BETWEEN THEOTHER 2 LINES ARE 2 DOTS.Lines and dots in patterns that hooded figure pointed to (Part 1)and said, "Remember this." Drawing © 2007 by Kansas abductee.

BELOW THAT, THERE ARE 2 CURVED LINES WITH A DOT ABOVE AND A DOTBELOW. THEN A TRIANGLE THAT HAS A CURVED LINE COMING OUT OF THECENTER WITH A DOT ABOVE AND A DOT BELOW THAT CURVED LINE.THEN THERE ARE 2 PARALLEL, SLIGHTLY CURVED LINES INTERSECTED BYANOTHER HORIZONTAL CURVED LINE AND A DOT ABOVE THE HORIZONTAL.WHERE DID YOU SEE THESE SYMBOLS? WHAT DO THEY MEAN?Those are what I was shown (by the hooded entity in the craft’s round room - See Part 1).What they mean, I’m not sure. I just know that I’m supposed to remember those.SO THESE WERE IMPRINTED ON YOUR MIND AS FOUR SYMBOLS THAT YOUWERE SUPPOSED TO REMEMBER AFTER THEY LIGHTED UP AND THEHOODED BEING POINTED AT THEM AND SAID, ‘REMEMBER THIS.’Correct.AS YOU LOOK AT EACH OF THOSE, DO YOU GET ANY IMPRESSION ABOUTWHAT THEY MEAN?It’s a code of some kind. Either they have shown me how to decipher it and consciously Idon’t remember? Or they have not shown me how to decipher it yet. Or, when I see thesymbols in a certain combination, I’ll know what it means.I have drawn them in different combinations, but I just can’t remember. And there’sprobably a lot more that I can’t consciously remember. This is the stuff I consciouslyremember. I’m just wondering how much I don’t consciously remember? Different Craft, Different SpeciesRectangular "mother ship" on left, used by the big nosed reptilians to transport fightingdiscs to Earth. Dumbbell craft linked to blond-haired, blue-eyed humanoids. Big nosed reptiliansalso associated with the large triangle with curved rear and small, raised dome on top.Drawings of different craft © 2007 by Kansas abductee.YOU DON’T HAVE A CLEAR IMPRESSION OF WHAT INTELLIGENCE IS IN THETRIANGULAR CRAFT IN YOUR SKETCHES?No.THE DUMBBELL IS ASSOCIATED WITH WHAT?I associate that with the blond-haired, blue-eyed people.THE DISCS ARE DEFINITELY?The big nosed lizard types. They are also associated with one of the triangular craft.IS THAT THE ONE IN THE MIDDLE WITH THE LITTLE DOME PIECE ON IT?Right.IF THOSE OTHER TRIANGULAR SHIPS HEADED TOWARD EARTH YOU DREW

ARE ASSOCIATED IN YOUR MIND WITH THE BLONDS, THEN THAT WOULDMEAN THE BLONDS AND LIZARDS HAVE SHIPS THAT LOOK ALMOST THESAME.Yeah, I see what you are saying.SO, HOW WOULD WE KNOW WHO IS IN WHAT?There’s probably some type of emblem, symbol...FREQUENCIES – I KNOW DIFFERENT CRAFT GIVE OFF DIFFERENTFREQUENCIES.Yeah, that would probably be how you would tell. Mysterious SymbolsLET’S MOVE DOWN TO THE MIDDLE. YOU’VE GOT THE WORD 'SYMBOLS.'Series of symbols not understood. Drawing © 2007 by Kansas abductee.ON THE LEFT, THERE IS A TRIANGLE WITH A CURVED SECTION OUT OF THEBOTTOM THAT HAS 3 CIRCLES IN A TRIANGLULAR PATTERN. THEN THERE ISA CIRCLE WITH A DOT. WHAT IS THAT?Those are symbols I was shown.YOU DON’T HAVE ANY MEANING FOR THEM?No, that’s the weird part. I can sit and draw them all day and nothing comes. I kind ofwonder – these came around the time that I was wearing that ring of my Dad’s. I kind ofwonder if the non-humans didn’t get me mixed up with my Dad or something. I don’tknow. Maybe I should have known what they meant when they showed them to me andthey realized I didn’t. I don’t know."
